---
title: Cal Smart Moroccan-Inspired Tofu with Jewelled Couscous and Fig Sauce
description: Sweet and savoury is the name of the game with this succulent, Moroccan-spiced tofu. They're topped with a delectable fig sauce and served alongside a bed of fluffy jewelled couscous.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R1037_W20_CA_RP157147-1_Main__2low-0e057f45.jpg
